title: Kannada Newspaper.apk
description:
Read Kannada newspapers in one app. Various newspapers from 
Karnataka are available.
Newspapers includes:
Kannada Prabha, Vijaya Karnataka, Varthabharathi, Sanjevani, Kranti Kannada Daily, Udayavani (Kannada for Morning Voice in Kannada), Samyukta Karnataka, Praja Pragathi, Janatha Madhyama, Sudharma, Suddi Moola, Kolaravani, Ee Sanje Kannada, SahilOnline (Kannada), Kannadaratna.com, kannada.oneindia.in, Webdunia (Kannada), Yahoo Kannada News, Kannada Thats Cricket, TV9 Bangalore etc
